name: TBey's 1st Custom Mari0 Mappack
body:
### My First Mari0 Mappack
I've been playing Mari0 for a while, and decided to create my custom mappack. It took me 3 months to complete, but now it's done.

### Features
 * Custom Tiles
 * 8 Worlds
 * Bosses
 * Puzzles
 * `Parts which require platforming skills`

### Authors and Contributors
This mappack is brought to you by @TBey, with the help of @xDAtom.

### Issues
Report issues on the [GitHub Issue Tracker](https://github.com/TBey/Mari0-Mappack-1/issues?state=open).
